%20while%20she%20was%20fleeing%20from%20her%20burning%20house%20with%20her%20two%20sons%2C%20niece%20and%20sister-in-law%20-%20and%20gang-raped%20on%20May%203%2C%20the%20day%20violence%20broke%20out%20in%20the%20district%20after%20a%20rally%20by%20the%20hill-majority%20Kukis%20over%20the%20valley-majority%20Meiteis'%20demand%20for%20inclusion%20under%20the%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(ST)%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20she%20mustered%20the%20courage%20to%20go%20to%20the%20police%20after%20seeing%20reports%20of%20women%20speaking%20up%20about%20the%20horrors%20they%20went%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20did%20not%20disclose%20the%20incident%20to%20save%20myself%20and%20my%20family's%20honour%2C%20dignity%20and%20to%20save%20ourselves%20from%20social%20ostracism.%20The%20delay%20in%20filing%20this%20complaint%20is%20due%20to%20social%20stigma...%20I%20even%20wanted%20to%20end%20myself%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20woman%20said%20in%20her%20statement%20attached%20with%20the%20'zero%20FIR'%20filed%20with%20Bishnupur%20police%20station%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20is%20now%20living%20in%20a%20relief%20camp%20for%20internally%20displaced%20people.%20The%20case%20has%20been%20filed%20under%20Sections%20376D%2C%20354%2C%20120B%20and%2034%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20(IPC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%2C%20at%206.30%20pm%20on%20May%203%2C%20miscreants%20started%20burning%20the%20woman%20and%20her%20neighbour's%20houses%2C%20after%20which%20she%2C%20her%20two%20sons%2C%20niece%20and%20sister-in-law%20ran%20as%20fast%20as%20they%20could.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20carried%20my%20niece%20on%20my%20back%20and%20also%20held%20my%20two%20sons%20and%20started%20running%20from%20the%20spot%20along%20with%20my%20sister-in-law.%20She%20was%20also%20carrying%20a%20baby%20on%20her%20back%20and%20running%20ahead%20of%20me.%20Then%20I%20stumbled%20and%20fell%20down%20on%20the%20road%20and%20unable%20to%20get%20up...%20my%20sister-in-law%20came%20back%20running%20towards%20me%20and%20picked%20up%20my%20niece%20from%20my%20back%20and%20ran%20along%20with%20my%20two%20sons%20as%20I%20insisted%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20woman%20said%20in%20the%20'zero%20FIR'%20filed%20in%20Bishnupur%2C%2035%20km%20from%20her%20now-destroyed%20house%20in%20Churachandpur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20finally%20managed%20to%20get%20up%2C%20some%20five-six...%20miscreants%20got%20hold%20of%20me...%20They%20started%20verbally%20abusing%20and%20assaulting%20me.%20Despite%20my%20resistance%2C%20I%20was%20forcefully%20pinned%20down.%20After%20this%2C%20the%20men%20started%20sexually%20assaulting%20me...%26quot%3B%20the%20woman%20said%20in%20the%20FIR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20'zero%20FIR'%20can%20be%20filed%20at%20any%20police%20station%2C%20not%20necessarily%20at%20a%20police%20station%20under%20whose%20jurisdiction%20the%20crime%20happened.%20The%20police%20station%20where%20the%20case%20has%20been%20filed%20has%20to%20send%20the%20FIR%20to%20the%20correct%20jurisdiction%2C%20which%20will%20then%20investigate%20it%2C%20in%20this%20case%20the%20police%20station%20in%20Churachandpur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20said%20her%20health%20completely%20deteriorated%2C%20and%20she%20even%20thought%20of%20dying%20by%20suicide.%20She%20said%20she%20went%20to%20the%20Regional%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Sciences%20in%20the%20state%20capital%20Imphal%2C%20but%20returned%20without%20seeing%20a%20doctor%20as%20she%20couldn't%20even%20%26quot%3Bexpress%26quot%3B%20herself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubsequently%2C%20she%20said%2C%20she%20went%20to%20JNIMS%20Hospital%20in%20Imphal%20on%20Tuesday%20as%20her%20health%20worsened.%20The%20doctors%20there%20treated%20and%20counselled%20her%2C%20contributing%20to%20her%20strength%20to%20report%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20I%20started%20realising%20the%20trauma%20and%20sufferings%20that%20I%20went%20through%20because%20of%20their%20heinous%20crimes%20committed%20against%20me%20without%20any%20fault%20of%20mine...%20Adequate%20punishment%20should%20be%20given%20to%20the%20gang%20of%20culprits%20who%20abused%2C%20sexually%20and%20physically%20assaulted%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20woman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20a%20horrific%20video%20of%20two%20women%20being%20paraded%20naked%20on%20a%20road%20by%20a%20group%20of%20men%20in%20Manipur%20was%20shared%20widely%20on%20social%20media%2C%20drawing%20massive%20condemnation%20and%20calls%20for%20action.%20The%20accused%20seen%20in%20the%20video%20have%20been%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Manipur%20Police%20told%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20over%206%2C500%20police%20cases%20have%20been%20filed%20between%20the%20nearly%20three-month%20period%20from%20May%203%20to%20July%2030.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20chunk%20of%20police%20cases%20has%20been%20filed%20under%20the%20category%20%26quot%3Barson%2C%20looting%20and%20destruction%20of%20house%20property%26quot%3B%2C%20according%20to%20a%20police%20report%20submitted%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20a%20copy%20of%20which%20NDTV%20has%20seen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20cases%20in%20thousands%2C%20inflated%20by%20multiple%20zero%20FIRs%20over%20the%20same%20cases%2C%20are%20arson%20(4%2C454)%2C%20looting%20(4%2C148)%2C%20destruction%20of%20house%20property%20(4%2C694)%2C%20and%20damage%20to%20public%20property%20(584).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20data%20indicates%20the%20huge%20scale%20of%20destruction%20of%20property%20in%20Manipur%20when%20the%20ethnic%20violence%20was%20at%20its%20worst.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691657220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2Fec1496o8_manipur-violence_625x300_28_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fi-fell-sister-in-law-ran-with-my-sons-another-manipur-gang-rape-horror-from-churachandpur-4285597%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Another%20horrific%20case%20o