20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEater%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20preemptive%20payments%20are%20meant%20to%20prevent%20people%20from%20not%20showing%20up%20to%20their%20reservations%2C%20and%20they%20differ%20from%20no-show%20fees%2C%20which%20are%20penalties%20that%20many%20restaurants%20enforce%20on%20diners%20%3Cem%3Eafter%3C%2Fem%3E%20they%20have%20ghosted%20their%20reservations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo-shows%20for%20restaurant%20reservations%20aren't%20new.%20In%202021%2C%20online%20reservation%20service%20OpenTable%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.opentable.com%2Fblog%2Fno-show-numbers%2F%5C%22%3Efound%3C%2Fa%3E%2028%25%20of%20Americans%20said%20they'd%20ghosted%20a%20restaurant%20reservation%20in%20the%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20the%20company%20launched%20a%20deposits%20feature%20on%20its%20reservation%20platform%20that%20allows%20restaurants%20to%20require%20payments%20with%20each%20booking.%20Restaurants%20on%20the%20platform%20choose%20whether%20to%20enforce%20the%20deposit%20on%20all%20reservations%20or%20on%20specific%20occasions%2C%20such%20as%20bookings%20for%20big%20parties%20or%20during%20peak%20hours%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20OpenTable%20said%20in%20an%20email%20to%20Insider.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReservation%20deposits%20vary%20in%20price%20and%20application%2C%20and%20the%20restaurants%20Insider%20spoke%20with%20said%20they%20either%20refund%20the%20upfront%20payment%20or%20deduct%20it%20from%20the%20final%20bill%20if%20the%20diner%20shows.%20Some%20eateries%20charge%20a%20flat%20deposit%20on%20a%20reservation%2C%20while%20others%20require%20money%20for%20each%20reserved%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJC%20Myska%2C%20general%20manager%20at%20Kintsugi%20Omakase%20in%20Manhattan%2C%20said%20his%20luxury%20restaurant's%20%2435-per-person%20reservation%20deposit%20is%20vital%20for%20the%20eatery%2C%20which%20has%20only%2010%20seats.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPearl%20Street%20Caviar%2C%20an%20importer%20and%20distributor%20of%20caviar%20in%20Brooklyn%2C%20New%20York%2C%20has%20a%20cafe%20that%20began%20implementing%20a%20blanket%20%2410%20deposit%20for%20reservations%20this%20spring%20to%20battle%20patrons%20ghosting%20reservations.%20Founder%20Craig%20Page%20said%20that%20the%20rate%20of%20no-shows%20has%20dropped%20significantly%20since%20the%20rollout%20of%20the%20charge%2C%20which%20gets%20deducted%20from%20the%20final%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20very%20few%20seats%2C%20and%20we%20plan%20and%20staff%20significantly%20around%20reservations%2C%26quot%3B%20Page%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20when%20people%20don't%20show%20up%2C%20it's%20not%20a%20disaster%2C%20it's%20just%20a%20bummer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20other%20restaurants%2C%20no-shows%20can%20be%20killer.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.opentable.com%2Fblog%2Fno-show-numbers%2F%5C%22%3EThe%202021%20OpenTable%20analysis%3C%2Fa%3E%20looked%20at%20Blackfish%2C%20a%2040-seat%20restaurant%20in%20Philadelphia%2C%20and%20found%20that%20if%20just%20six%20people%20did%20not%20show%20up%2C%20it%20would%20lose%205%25%20of%20its%20income%20%E2%80%94%20or%20a%20typical%20restaurant's%20profit%20margin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BRestaurants%20operate%20on%20razor%20thin%20profit%20margins%20and%20simply%20can't%20afford%20last-minute%20cancellations%20and%20no-shows%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20OpenTable%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%202020%2C%20acclaimed%20chefs%20called%20out%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Ftom-kerridge-criticizes-people-dont-show-up-for-dinner-reservations-2020-7%5C%22%3Ediners%20who%20did%20not%20show%20up%20for%20reservations%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20Michelin-star%20chef%20Tom%20Kerridge%20saying%20such%20customers%20endangered%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Page%20said%20Pearl%20Street%20Caviar's%20customers%20aren't%20shocked%20by%20the%20charge%20and%20that%20any%20confusion%20is%20usually%20cleared%20up%2C%20some%20diners%20have%20voiced%20their%20displeasure%20about%20reservation%20deposits%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Yelp%20user%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.yelp.com%2Fbiz%2Fmonkey-bar-new-york-4%3Fosq%3Dmonkey%2Bbar%26sort_by%3Ddate_desc%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eleft%20a%20positive%20review%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20New%20York%20City%20restaurant%20Monkey%20Bar%2C%20but%20said%20her%20%26quot%3Bonly%20complaint%26quot%3B%20was%20the%20%26quot%3Bnon-refundable%20fee%20to%20make%20the%20reservation%20on%20resy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMonkey%20Bar%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment%2C%20but%20the%20restaurant's%20website%20says%20there%20is%20a%20%242.50%20fee%20charged%20per%20person%20for%20reservations%20made%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20July%2C%20one%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2FFoodNYC%2Fcomments%2F154f6d0%2Fthoughts_on_monkey_bar_charging_for_reservations%2F%5C%22%3EReddit%20user%3C%2Fa%3E%20fretted%20over%20%26quot%3Bthe%20principle%20of%20a%20nonrefundable%20deposit%20for%20making%20a%20reservation%20online.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20alone%20probably%20wouldn't%20discourage%20me%20from%20booking%20a%20table%20at%20a%20place%20I%20really%20want%20to%20try%2C%20but%20it%20could%20definitely%20push%20me%20towards%20other%20options%20if%20I'm%20on%20the%20fence%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frestaurants-charging-nonrefundable-reservations-fees-deposits-to-battle-no-shows-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691657101000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d3ebd1ec14ba0019f390fa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frestaurants-charging-nonrefundable-reservations-fees-deposits-to-battle-no-shows-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Restaurants%20are%20charging%20up-front%20fees%20in%20order%20to%20book%20a%20table%20to%20discourage%20the%20practice%20of%20not%20showing%20up%20to%20reservations.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22grivera%40insider.com%20(Gabriel%20Rivera)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frestaurants-charging-nonrefundable-reservations-fees-deposits-to-battle-no-shows-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Isha%20on%20Ranveer%20replacing%20SRK%20in%20Don%203%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691656764000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102603014%2Cimgsize-24840.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fdon-actress-isha-koppikar-says-ranveer-singh-was-the-natural-choice-to-take-on-role-from-shah-rukh-khan%2Farticleshow%2F102602666.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F102602666.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EIsha%20Koppikar%2C%20who%20played%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20the%20Don%20franchise%2C%20has%20praised%20the%20casting%20of%20Ranveer%20Singh%20in%20'Don'.%20According%20to%20the%20actress%2C%20Singh%20is%20a%20natural%20choice%20to%20take%20on%20the%20role%20from%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%2C%20and%20his%20ability%20to%20adapt%20to%20his%20on-screen%20characters%20makes%20him%20deserving%20of%20the%20coveted%20role.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UPA%20Wasted%20A%20Decade%2C%20Every%20Crisis%20Changed%20To%20Reform%20Now%3A%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance%20(UPA)%20has%20wasted%20a%20decade%2C%20said%20Union%20Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20as%20she%20tore%20into%20the%20Opposition%20front%20while%20replying%20to%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%20in%20the%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20criticism%20of%20the%20UPA%2C%20the%20Opposition%20front%20which%20was%20in%20power%20during%202004-2014%20and%20is%20now%20known%20by%20the%20acronym%20'INDIA'%2C%20was%20followed%20by%20a%20report%20card%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Sitharaman%20said%20the%20UPA%20had%20no%20credibility%20and%20it%20reminded%20the%20people%20of%20corruption%20and%20cronyism%2C%20due%20to%20which%20the%20Opposition%20parties%20have%20chosen%20the%20'INDIA'%20name%20for%20their%20front.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E'INDIA'%20stands%20for%20Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance%2C%20and%20comprises%2026%20parties%2C%20including%20the%20Congress%2C%20Trinamool%2C%20DMK%2C%20RJD%2C%20and%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20also%20took%20a%20swipe%20at%20the%20contenders%20in%20the%20Opposition%20front%20and%20pointed%20out%20how%20they%20are%20opposed%20to%20each%20other%20in%20different%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20bizarre%20partnership.%20In%20Punjab%2C%20Congress%20and%20AAP%20are%20fighting.%20In%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Trinamool%2C%20Left%20and%20Congress%20are%20fighting.%20In%20Kerala%2C%20Left%20and%20Congress%20are%20fighting.%20In%20Jammu%20and%20Congress%2C%20National%20Conference%20and%20PDP%20are%20fighting%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20Finance%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20UPA%20has%20wasted%20a%20whole%20decade%2C%20but%20every%20crisis%20has%20changed%20to%20reform%20now.%20Under%20the%20NDA%2C%20we%20have%20seen%20high%20growth%20and%20low%20inflation%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20the%20Congress%20%26quot%3Bdynasty%26quot%3B%20was%20benefitting%20from%20leakages%20and%20major%20scams.%20%26quot%3BBut%20NDA%20has%20put%20an%20end%20to%20it.%20Rs%202.76%20lakh%20crore%20profit%20was%20recorded%20because%20we%20stopped%20the%20leakages%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENDA%2C%20or%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%2C%20is%20the%20ruling%20front%20led%20by%20Ms%20Sitharaman's%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20highlighted%20how%20her%20government%20has%20revolutionized%20the%20finance%20sector%20with%20the%20UPI%20(Unified%20Payments%20Interface).%20She%20said%20the%20government's%20policies%20support%20start-ups%20which%20have%20seen%20tremendous%20gains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20pointed%20to%20her%20government's%20focus%20on%20the%20healthcare%20system%20and%20that%20now%20there%20are%2023%20AIIMS%20in%20the%20country%2C%20as%20compared%20to%20just%20seven%20in%202014%2C%20when%20the%20Modi%20government%20was%20voted%20to%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20a%20dig%20at%20the%20previous%20UPA%20government%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BLaunching%20a%20scheme%20is%20easy%2C%20but%20implementing%20them%20is%20difficult.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20highlighted%20her%20government's%20efforts%20to%20tackle%20inflation%2C%20including%20the%20tomato%20prices%20that%20skyrocketed%20in%20the%20recent%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20imported%20tomatoes%20from%20Nepal.%20Delhi%20and%20National%20Capital%20Region%20(NCR)%20will%20get%20tomatoes%20at%20subsidised%20rates%20as%20low%20as%20Rs%2070.%20Opposition-ruled%20states%20have%20not%20lowered%20the%20price%20of%20fuel%2C%20as%20a%20result%20of%20which%20inflation%20pressures%20remain%20high%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESlamming%20the%20DMK%20that%20raked%20up%20the%20issue%20of%20women%20safety%20and%20used%20the%20term%20%26quot%3BDroupadi%26quot%3B%20to%20refer%20to%20an%20incident%20in%20violence-hit%20Manipur%2C%20she%20reminded%20them%20of%20a%201989%20incident%20in%20which%20former%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Chief%20Minister%20J%20Jayalalithaa%20(then%20leader%20of%20opposition)'s%20%26quot%3Bsaree%20was%20pul