id.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20seems%20to%20indicate%20that%20the%20drop%20in%20demand%20for%20TSLA%20vehicles%20was%20not%20driven%20by%20broader%20economic%20factors%20in%20China%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20it%20seems%20Tesla%20may%20have%20a%20China%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGrowing%20demand%20for%20BYD%20comes%20despite%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-economy-recession-inflation-deflation-xi-jinping-stimulus-cpi-ppi-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworsening%20economic%20backdrop%20in%20China%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20country's%20economy%20has%20slipped%20into%20deflation%2C%20with%20shop%20and%20factory%20prices%20both%20falling%20last%20month.%20The%20data%20is%20the%20latest%20red%20flag%20for%20Beijing%2C%20which%20is%20also%20struggling%20with%20stuttering%20growth%2C%20a%20property-sector%20crisis%2C%20and%20surging%20youth%20unemployment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-china-sales-tumble-price-cuts-byd-bofa-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691654401000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6365483600d7c60018783dd8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Ftesla-china-sales-tumble-price-cuts-byd-bofa-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22China's%20economic%20slump%20may%20not%20be%20the%20reason%20why%20demand%20for%20Teslas%20in%20China%20are%20waning%20%E2%80%93%20consumers%20are%20just%20flocking%20to%20local%20competitors.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ztayeb%40businessinsider.com%20(Zahra%20Tayeb)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Ftesla-china-sales-tumble-price-cuts-byd-bofa-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Enhypen-Backer%2C