dtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fnot-kl-rahul-or-shreyas-iyer-ex-india-star-backs-this-player-for-no-4-odi-spot-4282506%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fnot-kl-rahul-or-shreyas-iyer-ex-india-star-backs-this-player-for-no-4-odi-spot-4282506%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22P%26W%20Engines%20Issue%20To%20Have%20Minimal%20Impact%20On%20IndiGo%20Fleet%3A%20Aviation%20Body%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAviation%20regulator%20DGCA%20today%20said%20material%20anomalies%20detected%20in%20certain%20Pratt%20%26amp%3B%20Whitney%20engines%20will%20have%20a%20%26quot%3Bminimal%26quot%3B%20impact%20on%20IndiGo%20fleet%20as%20only%20two%20operational%20engines%20of%20the%20airline%20will%20be%20required%20to%20be%20removed%20for%20inspection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20a%20total%20of%2015%20engines%20powering%20IndiGo%20planes%20will%20be%20impacted%2C%2013%20of%20them%20are%20currently%20non-operational%2C%20according%20to%20a%20senior%20official%20at%20the%20Directorate%20General%20of%20of%20Civil%20Aviation%20(DGCA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndiGo%20is%20the%20largest%20customer%20of%20the%20A320%20planes%20and%20the%20aircraft%20are%20powered%20by%20P%26amp%3BW%20engines.%20Grounded%20carrier%20Go%20First's%20A320%20neo%20fleet%20are%20also%20having%20P%26amp%3BW%20engines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20US-based%20P%26amp%3BW%20said%20it%20has%20found%20that%20a%20rare%20condition%20in%20powdered%20metal%20used%20to%20manufacture%20certain%20engine%20parts%20may%20reduce%20the%20life%20of%20those%20parts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EP%26amp%3BW%20had%20said%20the%20material%20anomalies%20would%20impact%20around%201%2C002%20PW1100G%20engines%20worldwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20engine%20maker%20has%20now%20issued%20the%20Service%20Instructions%20(SI)%20enlisting%20the%20serial%20numbers%20of%20the%20engine%20series%20which%20are%20required%20to%20be%20removed%20for%20performing%20Angle%20Ultrasonic%20Scan%20Inspection%20(AUSI)%20during%20the%20shop%20visit%20and%20accordingly%20are%20required%20to%20be%20removed%20before%20September%2015%2C%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20impact%20of%20this%20Service%20Instruction%20on%20the%20fleet%20of%20IndiGo%2C%20as%20ascertained%20from%20them%2C%20is%20minimal%20and%20only%202%20engines%20which%20are%20currently%20operational%20in%20their%20fleet%20would%20be%20required%20to%20be%20removed%20out%20of%20a%20total%20of%2013%20affected%20engines%20(of%20which%2011%20are%20currently%20non-operational).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20implies%20that%20there%20would%20be%20little%20or%20no%20impact%20on%20the%20capacity%20of%20Indian%20carriers%20during%20the%20ensuing%20high%20season%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20IndiGo's%20quarterly%20earnings%20call%20on%20August%202%2C%20IndiGo%20CEO%20Pieter%20Elbers%20had%20said%20%26quot%3Bsingle%20digit%26quot%3B%20number%20of%20P%26amp%3BW%20engines%20will%20be%20impacted%20in%20the%20first%20phase.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20new%20issue%20that%20has%20been%20highlighted%20by%20the%20OEM.%20Here%20we%20have%20to%20rely%20on%20the%20communication%20which%20was%20shared%20by%20P%26amp%3BW%20about%20certain%20probable%20manufacturing%20anomalies%20which%20are%20actually%20leading%20to%20additional%20inspection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20We%20don't%20know%20yet%20what%20is%20going%20to%20be%20the%20precise%20impact%20in%20the%20first%20phase...%20but%20of%20course%20we%20are%20in%20clear%20contact%20and%20clear%20coordination%20with%20P%26amp%3BW%20to%20see%20what%20is%20going%20to%20be%20the%20precise%20impact%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElbers%20had%20also%20said%20there%20are%20still%20a%20lot%20of%20questions%20on%20the%20precise%20duration%20and%20phasing%20of%20the%20inspection%20of%20engines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EP%26amp%3BW%20is%20already%20grappling%20with%20s