20Opposition%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20a%20Union%20Cabinet%20Minister%20nominated%20by%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bill%20appears%20to%20dilute%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20March%202023%20judgment%20in%20which%20a%20Constitution%20bench%20said%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioners%20and%20Election%20Commissioners%20must%20be%20appointed%20on%20the%20advice%20of%20a%20panel%20comprising%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20and%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judgment%20said%20this%20arrangement%20would%20continue%20until%20parliament%20came%20out%20with%20a%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bill%20states%20that%20the%20search%20committee%20-%20which%20will%20identify%20five%20names%20to%20be%20considered%20by%20the%20PM-led%20panel%20-%20will%20comprise%20the%20Cabinet%20Secretary%20and%20two%20other%20secretaries%20of%20the%20Centre.%20The%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20and%20Election%20Commissioners%2C%20it%20states%2C%20should%20hold%20or%20have%20held%20a%20post%20equivalent%20to%20the%20rank%20of%20a%20secretary%20in%20the%20Government%20of%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20the%20Delhi%20Special%20Police%20Establishment%20Act%2C%20also%20brought%20after%20a%20similar%20Supreme%20Court%20ruling%20in%202014%2C%20had%20retained%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20in%20the%20selection%20committee%20to%20appoint%20a%20CBI%20Director.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fresh%20Bill%20sets%20up%20another%20confrontation%20between%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20the%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20judges'%20appointments%20to%20controversial%20laws%20such%20as%20Delhi%20services%20Act%2C%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20have%20been%20locked%20in%20a%20tussle%20over%20several%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20and%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20have%20also%20differed%20in%20their%20positions%20on%20issues%20such%20as%20the%20basic%20structure%20doctrine%3B%20simply%20put%2C%20it%20means%20the%20Constitution%20has%20a%20basic%20structure%20that%20cannot%20be%20changed%20by%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691652000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-09%2F5u6qtss_rajya-sabha-generic-pti-photo_625x300_23_September_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentres-bill-on-appointment-of-poll-body-chief-removes-chief-justice-from-panel-to-be-tabled-in-rajya-sabha-today-4285403%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20move%20likely%20to%20trigger%20a%20fresh%20face-off%20between%20the%20government%20and%20the%20judiciary%2C%20the%20Centre%20is%20set%20to%20push%20legislation%20that%20will%20exclude%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20from%20the%20process%20to%20appoint%20the%20country's%20top%20election%20officers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentres-bill-on-appointment-of-poll-body-chief-removes-chief-justice-from-panel-to-be-tabled-in-rajya-sabha-today-4285403%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentres-bill-on-appointment-of-poll-body-chief-removes-chief-justice-from-panel-to-be-tabled-in-rajya-sabha-today-4285403%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentres-bill-on-appointment-of-poll-body-chief-removes-chief-justice-from-panel-to-be-tabled-in-rajya-sabha-today-4285403%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Cardi%20B's%20microphone%20fetches%20%24100K%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691651506000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102601222%2Cimgsize-39044.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fmusic%2Fnews%2Fcardi-bs-microphone-thrown-at-fan-fetches-whopping-100k-in-charity-auction%2Farticleshow%2F102600389.cms%22%