cts.%20The%20actor%20is%20currently%20looking%20forward%20to%20'OMG%202'%20alongside%20Yami%20Gautam%20and%20Akshay%20Kumar.%20The%20movie%20has%20been%20creating%20a%20lot%20of%20buzz%20recently%20and%20is%20all%20set%20to%20hit%20theatres%20soon%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fexclusive-pankaj-tripathi-recalls-a-time-when-shah-rukh-khan-hosted-a-party-in-goa-reveals-the-best-quality-of-akshay-kumar-watch%2Farticleshow%2F102600129.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22RBI's%20Big%20Relief%20For%20Home%2C%20Auto%20Loan%20Takers%20With%20Choice%20Over%20Interest%20Type%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Reserve%20Bank%20today%20said%20it%20will%20come%20out%20with%20a%20framework%20allowing%20borrowers%20to%20switch%20to%20fixed%20interest%20rate%20from%20floating%20interest%20rate%2C%20a%20move%20that%20would%20provide%20relief%20to%20borrowers%20of%20home%2C%20auto%20and%20other%20loans%20reeling%20under%20the%20impact%20of%20high%20interest%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnveiling%20the%20bi-monthly%20monetary%20policy%2C%20Reserve%20Bank%20Governor%20Shaktikanta%20Das%20said%20under%20the%20framework%2C%20to%20be%20put%20in%20place%20shortly%2C%20the%20lenders%20will%20have%20to%20clearly%20communicate%20with%20the%20borrowers%20about%20tenor%20and%20EMI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20supervisory%20reviews%20undertaken%20by%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20and%20the%20feedback%20and%20references%20from%20members%20of%20public%20have%20revealed%20several%20instances%20of%20unreasonable%20elongation%20of%20tenor%20of%20floating%20rate%20loans%20by%20lenders%20without%20proper%20consent%20and%20communication%20to%20the%20borrowers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20address%20the%20issue%2C%20it%20is%20proposed%20to%20put%20in%20place%20a%20proper%20conduct%20framework%20to%20be%20implemented%20by%20all%20Regulated%20entities%20to%20address%20the%20issues%20faced%20by%20borrowers%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20framework%20envisages%20that%20lenders%20should%20clearly%20communicate%20with%20the%20borrowers%20for%20resetting%20the%20tenor%20and%2For%20EMI%2C%20provide%20options%20of%20switching%20to%20fixed%20rate%20loans%20or%20foreclosure%20of%20loans%2C%20transparent%20disclosure%20of%20various%20charges%20incidental%20to%20the%20exercise%20of%20these%20options%2C%20and%20proper%20communication%20of%20key%20information%20to%20the%20borrowers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20detailed%20guidelines%20in%20this%20regard%20would%20be%20issued%20shortly%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20enable%20the%20Infrastructure%20Debt%20Funds%20to%20play%20a%20greater%20role%20in%20financing%20of%20the%20infrastructure%20sector%20and%20to%20move%20towards%20the%20regulatory%20objective%20of%20harmonisation%20of%20regulations%20applicable%20to%20various%20categories%20of%20NBFCs%2C%20Das%20said%20a%20review%20of%20the%20extant%20regulatory%20framework%20for%20IDFs%20has%20been%20undertaken%20in%20consultation%20with%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20revised%20framework%20envisages%20withdrawal%20of%20the%20requirement%20of%20a%20sponsor%20for%20the%20IDFs%3B%20permission%20to%20finance%20Toll%20Operate%20Transfer%20projects%20(ToT)%20as%20direct%20lenders%2C%20access%20to%20ECBs%3B%20and%20making%20tripartite%20agreement%20optional%20for%20PPP%20projects%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Infrastructure%20Debt%20Fund%20was%20created%20as%20a%20separate%20category%20of%20NBFCs%20in%202011.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20rapid%20progress%20in%20digitalization%2C%20Das%20said%20India%20has%20embraced%20the%20concept%20of%20digital%20public%20infrastructure%20which%20encourages%20FinTech%20companies%20and%20startups%20to%20create%20and%20provide%20innovative%20solutions%20in%20payments%2C%20credit%2C%20and%20other%20financial%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20digital%20credit%20delivery%2C%20the%20data%20required%20for%20credit%20appraisal%20are%20available%20with%20different%20entities%20like%20Central%20and%20State%20governments%2C%20account%20aggregators%2C%20banks%2C%20credit%20information%20companies%2C%20digital%20identity%20authorities%2C%20etc%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20said%2C%20they%20are%20in%20separate%20systems%2C%20creating%20hindrance%20in%20frictionless%20and%20timely%20delivery%20of%20rule-based%20lending.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20address%20this%20situation%2C%20a%20pilot%20project%20for%20digitalisation%20of%20Kisan%20Credit%20Card%20(KCC)%20loans%20of%20less%20than%20Rs%201.60%20lakh%20was%20started%20in%20September%202022%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pilot%20tested%20end-to-end%20digitalisation%20of%20the%20lending%20process%20in%20a%20paperless%20and%20hassle-free%20manner.%20The%20KCC%20pilot%20is%20currently%20underway%20in%20select%20districts%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20UP%2C%20Maharashtra%20and%20the%20initial%20results%20are%20encouraging.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pilot%20also%20enables%20doorstep%20disbursement%20of%20loans%20in%20assisted%20or%20self-service%20mode%20without%20any%20paperwork.%20A%20similar%20pilot%20is%20being%20carried%20out%20for%20dairy%20loans%20based%20on%20milk%20pouring%20data%20with%20Amul%20in%20Gujarat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20the%20learnings%20from%20the%20above%20pilots%20and%20to%20expand%20the%20scope%20to%20all%20types%20of%20digital%20loans%2C%20he%20said%2C%20a%20digital%20Public%20Tech%20Platform%20is%20being%20developed%20by%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20Innovation%20Hub%20(RBIH).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Platform%20would%20enable%20delivery%20of%20frictionless%20credit%20by%20facilitating%20seamless%20flow%20of%20required%20digital%20information%20to%20lenders%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20end-to-end%2