ltiple%20large%20hotels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20like%20an%20area%20was%20bombed.%20It's%20like%20a%20war%20zone%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20helicopter%20pilot%20Richard%20Olsten%2C%20according%20to%20Hawaii%20News%20Now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20firefighters%20battling%20three%20major%20blazes%2C%20western%20Maui%20was%20closed%20to%20all%20but%20emergency%20workers%20and%20evacuees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22a51napao%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fa51napao_hawaii-wild-fire-3_625x300_10_August_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmergency%20services%20were%20overwhelmed%20by%20a%20disaster%20that%20appeared%20to%20have%20erupted%20almost%20without%20warning%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fires%2C%20which%20started%20Tuesday%20night%2C%20also%20scorched%20parts%20of%20the%20Big%20Island%20of%20Hawaii.%20The%20state%20said%20thousands%20of%20acres%20burned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%204%2C000%20tourists%20were%20trying%20to%20leave%20western%20Maui%2C%20said%20Ed%20Sniffen%20of%20the%20Hawaii%20Department%20of%20Transportation.%20Though%20at%20least%2016%20roads%20were%20closed%2C%20the%20Maui%20airport%20was%20operating%20fully%20and%20airlines%20were%20dropping%20fares%20and%20offering%20waivers%20to%20get%20people%20off%20the%20island%2C%20Sniffen%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPanicked%20evacuees%20posted%20images%20on%20social%20media%20showing%20clouds%20of%20smoke%20billowing%20over%20once-idyllic%20beaches%20and%20palm%20trees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20the%20last%20one%20off%20the%20dock%20when%20the%20firestorm%20came%20through%20the%20banyan%20trees%20and%20took%20everything%20with%20it.%20And%20I%20just%20ran%20out%20and%20helped%20everyone%20I%20could%20along%20the%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dustin%20Johnson%2C%20who%20was%20in%20Lahaina%20Harbor%20working%20for%20a%20charter%20boat%20company%20that%20offers%20two-hour%20tours.%20He%20spoke%20from%20Kahului%