d%20also%20like%20a%20caste%20census%20in%20Rajasthan%20so%20that%20those%20marginalised%20can%20benefit%20from%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Chief%20Minister%20Gehlot%20said%20at%20a%20Congress%20rally%20in%20Banswara%20organised%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20International%20Day%20of%20the%20World's%20Indigenous%20Peoples%2C%20or%20World%20Tribal%20Day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20also%20addressed%20the%20rally%2C%20effectively%20kickstarting%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20Congress's%20campaign%20for%20the%20assembly%20polls%20in%20Rajasthan%20scheduled%20later%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20powerful%20groups%20like%20the%20Jats%20raised%20concerns%20about%20discrepancies%20in%20the%20OBC%20reservation.%20They%20were%20backed%20by%20Mr%20Gehlot's%20own%20cabinet%20minister%2C%20Harish%20Chaudhary.%20The%20issue%20was%20resolved%20after%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20stepped%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister's%20desire%20to%20raise%20OBC%20reservation%20from%2021%25%20to%2027%25%20and%20earmark%20an%20additional%206%25%20for%20the%20most%20backward%20classes%20within%20the%20OBC%20community%20would%20take%20the%20reservation%20ceiling%20well%20above%2070%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20Rajasthan%20has%20a%20reservation%20of%2064%25%2C%20with%2021%25%20for%20OBCs%2C%2016%25%20for%20SCs%2C%2012%25%20for%20STs%2C%2010%25%20for%20EWS%2C%20and%205%25%20for%20MBCs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reservation%20conundrum%20has%20become%20a%20political%20challenge%20for%20governments%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20with%20groups%20within%20the%20quota%20system%20vying%20for%20more%20representation%20and%20influence.%20The%20violent%20Gujjar%20agitation%20for%20reservation%20is%20one%20example%20of%20this%2C%20as%20the%20Gujjars%20eventually%20settled%20after%20being%20granted%20reservation%20in%20the%20MBC%20quota.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20uncertain%20whether%20Chief%20Minister%20Gehlot%20will%20be%20able%20to%20navigate%20the%20complicated%20reservation%20matrix%2C%20as%20it%20is%20possible%20that%20other%20groups%20outside%20the%20reservation%20ambit%20could%20challenge%20any%20decision%20in%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20now%2C%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20ambitious%20announcement%20to%20consolidate%20the%20OBC%20vote%20bank%20in%20his%20favor%20ahead%20of%20the%20polls%20may%20only%20remain%20a%20poll%20promise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Gehlot%20also%20announced%20the%20%26quot%3BIndira%20Gandhi%20Free%20Smartphone%20Yojana%202023%26quot%3B%2C%20an%20initiative%20aimed%20at%20providing%20free%20smartphones%20to%20women%2C%20along%20with%20free%20internet%20and%20voice%20call%20services.%20Around%2040%20lakh%20women%20are%20expected%20to%20benefit%20from%20the%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22hi%5C%22%3E40%20%E0%A4%B2%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%96%20%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%B9%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%B2%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%93%E0%A4%82%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%8B%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%9F%E0%A4%AB%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%A8%20!%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%93%E0%A4%82%2C%20%E0%A4%AC%E0%A4%B9%E0%A4%A8%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%82%2C%20%E0%A4%AC%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%9F%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%AF%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%82%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%B6%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%BE%2C%20%E0%A4%9C%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%82%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%94%E0%A4%B0%20%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%B2%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%8F%20%E0%A4%AA%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%A6%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%B6%20%E0%A4%AE%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%82%20400%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%85%E0%A4%A7%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%95%20%E0%A4%AE%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%AC%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%87%E0%A4%B2%20%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%A3%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%82%E0%A4%A6%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%82%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%89%E0%A4%A6%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%98%E0%