0some%20more%20donations%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20construct%20a%20safe%20haven%20for%20animals.%20The%20Almighty%20Animal%20Care%20Trust%20was%20inaugurated%20in%202019%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20his%20cause%20started%20with%20taking%20care%20of%20stray%20dogs%2C%20his%20care%20soon%20expanded%20to%20other%20animals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20realised%20that%20in%20Chennai%2C%20there%20were%20sanctuaries%20for%20dogs%2C%20but%20when%20it%20came%20to%20farm%20animals%2C%20they%20had%20nowhere%20to%20go.%20Many%20bulls%2C%20buffaloes%20and%20calves%20are%20abandoned%20by%20their%20owners.%20They%20roam%20in%20the%20city%2C%20consume%20polluted%20water%20and%20food%2C%20and%20end%20up%20in%20difficult%20conditions%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESai%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20a%20dog%20gets%20hit%20by%20a%20car%2C%20there%20is%20a%20chance%20it%20will%20get%20some%20kind%20of%20help.%20However%2C%20with%20animals%20like%20sheep%2C%20cows%20and%20buffaloes%2C%20they%20are%20most%20likely%20to%20end%20up%20in%20slaughterhouses.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20led%20Sai%20to%20open%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F316625%2Fruvuotuo-belho-builds-mini-zoo-in-kohima-nagaland-saves-birds-and-animals-from-hunting%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eup%20the%20sanctuary%20to%20any%20animal%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20needs%20help.%20Presently%2C%20he%20has%20around%20250%20animals%20under%20his%20care%20%E2%80%94%20which%20include%20around%2080%20dogs%2C%2025%20goats%2C%20116%20cows%2C%20buffaloes%20and%20bulls%2C%204%20pigs%2C%20and%202%20horses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ERescuing%20and%20fighting%20for%20animal%20rights%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeople%20reach%20out%20to%20Sai%20via%20his%20Facebook%20and%20Instagram%20pages%20to%20inform%20him%20about%20any%20animal%20in%20danger.%20Some%20volunteers%20usually%20accompany%20him%20to%20rescue%20the%20animals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnce%20the%20animal%20is%20under%20our%20care%2C%20we%20immediately%20take%20it%20to%20a%20vet.%20After%20initial%20treatment%2C%20we%20take%20the%20animal%20to%20the%20sanctuary.%20There%2C%20we%20have%20a%20vet%20who%20visits%20every%20morning%20to%20check%20up%20on%20the%20animals%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCsq5eFlpAYb%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCsq5eFlpAYb%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCsq5eFlpAYb%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Sai%20Vignesh%20(%40saivignesh2000)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20taking%20care%20of%20the%20animals%20and%20giving%20them%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F286180%2Fhow-to-make-animal-dog-bird-shelter-help-for