that%20parts%20of%20his%20speech%20were%20expunged%20from%20Lok%20Sabha%20records.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnion%20minister%20Smriti%20Irani%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20accused%20Gandhi%20of%20%E2%80%9Cmisogyny%E2%80%9D%20after%20he%20allegedly%20threw%20a%20%E2%80%9Cflying%20kiss%E2%80%9D%20in%20her%20direction.%20Congress%20has%20disputed%20this.%20Opposition%20members%20have%20also%20accused%20Sansad%20TV%20of%20not%20showing%20Gandhi%20during%20his%20speech.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20debate%20on%20ethnic%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20on%20Wednesday%20veered%20towards%20the%20question%20of%20a%20plebiscite%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20second%20day%20of%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%20debate%20continued%20for%20over%20seven%20hours%20and%20saw%20enthusiastic%20speeches%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.thewire.in%2Farticle%2Fpolitics%2Famit-shah-defends-biren-singh-in-parliament%3Futm%3Dauthorlistpage%5C%22%3EUnion%20ministers%20Amit%20Shah%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Smriti%20Irani%20along%20with%20several%20members%20of%20the%20opposition%20INDIA%20alliance.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EParts%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20speech%20expunged%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGandhi%20opened%20the%20debate%20on%20Wednesday%20with%20a%20scathing%20attack%20on%20Modi%20for%20his%20silence%20on%20the%20ongoing%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20and%20accused%20him%20of%20being%20%E2%80%9Canti-national%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cmurdering%20India%20in%20Manipur.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20on%20Wednesday%20night%2C%20Lok%20Sabha%20records%20showed%20that%20parts%20of%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20speech%20had%20been%20expunged.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20total%2024%20words%20have%20been%20expunged%20from%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20speech.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20includes%20two%20implicit%20mentions%20of%20Speaker%20Om%20Prakash%20Birla%2C%20as%20Gandhi%20referred%20to%20billionaire%20businessman%20Gautam%20Adani.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBecause%20I%20focused%20on%20Adani%2C%20your%20senior%20leader%20must%20have%20felt%20anguished%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gandhi%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CHis%20anguish%20must%20have%20had%20its%20effect%20on%20you%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBoth%20these%20apparent%20references%20to%20Birla%20have%20been%20expunged.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20addition%2C%20the%20words%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Ehatya%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20(murder)%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Ekatl%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98%20(murder)%2C%20and%20%E2%80%98murder%E2%80%99%20have%20also%20been%20expunged%20wherever%20Gandhi%20has%20referred%20to%20Modi%20%E2%80%9Cmurdering%E2%80%9D%20India%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20his%20speech%20Gandhi%20had%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CYou%20have%20murdered%20that%20voice.%20This%20means%20you%20have%20murdered%20Bharat%20Mata%20in%20Manipur.%20By%20killing%20the%20people%20of%20Manipur%20you%20have%20murdered%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20addition%2C%20the%20words%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Edeshdrohi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(traitor%20to%20one%E2%80%99s%20country)%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Ehatyare%3C%2Fem%3E%20(murderer)%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Emara%3C%2Fem%3E%20(killed)%E2%80%99%20have%20also%20been%20expunged.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20are%20anti-national%2C%20you%20cannot%20be%20patriotic%2C%20you%20cannot%20be%20loving%20this%20country.%20You%20have%20murdered%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20had%20said%20in%20Hindi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESansad%20TV%20Cameras%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOpposition%20MPs%20have%20accused%20Sansad%20TV%20of%20not%20showing%20members%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20when%20they%20are%20s