he%20transfer%20of%20authority%20to%20the%20Provincial%20Councils%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20result%2C%20I%20propose%20that%20it%20might%20be%20more%20practical%20for%20us%20to%20initially%20focus%20on%20reaching%20consensus%20concerning%20other%20powers.%20It%E2%80%99s%20advisable%20to%20progress%20step%20by%20step%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWickremesinghe%20added%20that%20%E2%80%9Cprioritising%20sensitive%20matters%20could%20potentially%20hinder%20the%20attainment%20of%20any%20mutual%20agreement%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%2013%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20constitutional%20amendment%20was%20a%20result%20of%20the%201987%20India-Sri%20Lanka%20accord%20which%20led%20to%20the%20creation%20of%20provinces%20and%20devolution%20of%20land%20and%20police%20powers%20to%20the%20elected%20provincial%20councils.%20While%20the%20provinces%20have%20been%20created%2C%20the%20powers%20of%20land%20and%20police%20have%20still%20not%20been%20devolved%20due%20to%20opposition%20from%20all%20the%20Sinhala%20political%20parties.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20has%20repeatedly%20called%20for%20the%20full%20implementation%20of%20the%2013%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20amendment%2C%20which%20was%20also%20reiterated%20during%20Wickremesinghe%E2%80%99s%20visit%20to%20New%20Delhi%20last%20month.%20Ahead%20of%20the%20visit%2C%20Sri%20Lankan%20Tamil%20lawmakers%20had%20written%20to%20the%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20to%20ask%20him%20to%20pressurise%20Wickremesinghe%20on%20the%20implementation%20of%2013%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20amendment%20and%20holding%20the%20much-delayed%20provincial%20council%20elections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20returning%20to%20Colombo%2C%20Wikremesinghe%20had%20convened%20an%20all-party%20conference%20over%20the%20issue%20of%20r