ir%20first-ever%20World%20Cup%2C%20they%20achieved%20major%C2%A0milestones%3B%20winning%20their%20maiden%20match%2C%20seeing%20Nouhaila%20Benzina%20become%20the%20first%20player%20to%20take%20the%20field%20at%20the%20tournament%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fworld-cup-how-the-hijab-became-tournament-ready%2Fa-66353621%5C%22%3Ewearing%20a%20hijab%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20advancing%20to%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fwomens-world-cup-marocco-germany%2Fa-66429367%5C%22%3Eknockout%20stages%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20Germany%20with%20a%201-0%20victory%20over%20Colombia.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgainst%20France%2C%20they%20were%20outclassed%20in%20a%204-0%20loss%2C%20though%20the%20team%E2%80%99s%20disappointment%20should%20be%20shortlived%20after%20already%20overachieving.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGoing%20into%20the%20game%20we%20had%20all%20the%20belief%20that%20we%E2%80%99d%20be%20able%20to%20progress%20through%20to%20the%20next%20round%2C%E2%80%9D%C2%A0Rosella%20Ayane%20told%20%3Cem%3EDW%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%E2%80%9CBut%20once%20we%20sit%20back%20and%20reflect%2C%20I%20think%20we%E2%80%99ll%20be%20super%20proud%20of%20ourselves%20for%20what%20we%E2%80%99ve%20achieved%20in%20this%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNo%20one%20expected%20us%20to%20get%20out%20of%20the%20group%20but%20we%20did%20it%20in%20our%20first-ever%20World%20Cup.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20Colombia%20win%2C%20Knorr%2C%20a%20bouillon%20company%20and%20a%20staple%20of%20the%20Moroccan%20kitchen%2C%20ran%20an%20advertisement%20with%20a%20picture%20of%20the%20World%20Cup%20trophy%20and%20a%20message%20that%20read%3A%20%E2%80%9CNothing%20other%20than%20Knorr%20belongs%20in%20the%20kitchen.%20Congratulations%20to%20the%20Lionesses%20of%20the%20Atlas.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBenzina%2C%20too%2C%20offered%20yet%20more%20recognition%20for%20athletes%20and%20young%20girls%20who%20wear%20hijabs%2C%20as%20the%2025-ye