e%20is%20no%20need%20to%20change%20him%20amid%20the%20ongoing%20violence%20in%20the%20state%20as%20he%20has%20been%20%E2%80%9Ccooperative%20with%20the%20Centre%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20the%20second%20day%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fparliament-congress-no-confidence-modi-speaker%5C%22%3Eno-confidence%20motion%20brought%20against%20the%20Modi%20government%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20Shah%20in%20his%20over%20two-hour-long%20speech%20listed%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20achievements%20for%20an%20hour%20and%2020%20minutes%2C%20and%20devoted%20around%2045%20minutes%20to%20explaining%20how%20the%20Union%20government%20is%20handling%20the%20violence%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManipur%20has%20been%20in%20the%20grip%20of%20ethnic%20violence%20since%20May%203.%20Over%20150%20people%20have%20died%20and%20tens%20of%20thousands%20displaced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20no-confidence%20motion%20was%20brought%20by%20the%20Congress%20on%20July%2026%20to%20make%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20address%20the%20violence%20in%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Flok-sabha-debates-no-confidence-motion-even-as-pm-modi-absent%5C%22%3EModi%20remained%20absent%20on%20both%20the%20days%20of%20the%20debate%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20is%20only%20expected%20to%20speak%20in%20the%20house%20on%20Thursday%20(August%2010).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPM%20has%20called%20me%20at%204%20am%20and%20woken%20me%20up%20at%206.30%20am%20as%20well%20%5Bto%20discuss%20Manipur%5D.%20And%20they%20are%20saying%20that%20the%20PM%20does%20not%20care%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Shah%2C%20responding%20to%20the%20opposition%E2%80%99s%20charge%20on%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20silence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C36%2C000%20central%20forces%20have%20been%20sent.%20The%20chief%20secretary%20has%20been%20changed%2C%20the%20DGP%20has%20been%20changed%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2F