%3F%20And%20they%20are%20asking%20why%20the%20PM%20has%20not%20visited%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%20appealed%20to%20both%20the%20Meiteis%20and%20Kukis%20to%20maintain%20peace%20and%20come%20to%20the%20discussion%20table%20with%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20end%20the%20violence%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20appeal%20to%20both%20the%20Meitei%20and%20Kuki%20communities%20to%20begin%20a%20dialogue.%20Violence%20is%20not%20the%20answer.%20We%20assure%20you%20that%20we%20will%20bring%20peace%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20motion%20was%20also%20moved%20by%20speaker%20Om%20Birla%20in%20the%20house%20appealing%20for%20peace%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EWatch%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-full-details-kuki-leaders-talks-amit-shah-karan-thapar%5C%22%3EFull%20Details%20of%20Kuki%20Leaders%E2%80%99%20Talks%20With%20Amit%20Shah%20on%20Mass%20Burials%2C%20Separate%20Administration%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo-confidence%20motion%20%E2%80%98politically%20motivated%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%2C%20Shah%20listed%20his%20government%E2%80%99s%20achievements%20and%20said%20that%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Cpolitically%20motivated%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%20bring%20a%20no-confidence%20motion%2C%20it%20is%20a%20question%20mark%20on%20the%20government.%20And%20that%20is%20why%20I%20have%20to%20give%20my%20government%E2%80%99s%20report%20card%2C%20because%20this%20is%20politically%20motivated%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%20said%20that%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%20has%20been%20brought%20to%20%E2%80%9Cmislead%20the%20nation%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20last%20nine%20years%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20taken%20over%2050%20landmark%20decisions%20for%20the%20nation.%20Today%20is%20August%209%2C%20and%20on%20this%20day%2C