anipur-conflict-national-identity-northeast-kashmir%5C%22%3Esilence%20on%20the%20Manipur%20violence%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20shown%20that%20the%20leaders%20are%20bound%2C%20ideologically%20enough%2C%20to%20carry%20the%20weight%20of%20the%20honorific.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20first%20Lok%20Sabha%20speech%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20August%209%2C%20after%20his%20reinstatement%20as%20a%20member%20of%20parliament%20is%20a%20valid%20case.%20He%20did%20not%20merely%20speak%20as%20a%20Congress%20leader%20but%20as%20an%20alliance%20leader%20steering%20the%20ideological%20beliefs%20of%20INDIA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%2037-minute%20speech%20was%20as%20much%20an%20attack%20on%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20nationalist%20credentials%20as%20on%20its%20claim%20of%20delivering%20corruption-free%20governance.%20The%20Congress%20leader%20not%20only%20laid%20down%20how%20INDIA%20parties%20considered%20%E2%80%9CBharat%E2%80%9D%20as%20a%20union%20of%20diverse%20and%20equal%20voices%20but%20also%20how%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20decisions%20have%20been%20largely%20controlled%20by%20corporate%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F5VuCxPNaLf0%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20each%20of%20his%20attacks%2C%20Gandhi%20also%20responded%20to%20the%20barrage%20of%20criticisms%20that%20INDIA%20parties%20have%20faced%20over%20the%20last%20few%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeriding%20the%20INDIA%20group%2C%20Modi%20had%20recently%20said%20that%20the%20group%20should%20be%20called%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fghamandia-pm-modi-takes-dig-at-opposition-alliance-ahead-of-no-confidence-motion-2417853-2023-08-08%5C%22%3Eghamandiya%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E(arrogant)%20instead%20of%20INDIA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGandhi%20responded%20to%20the%20prime%20minister%20by%20reminding%20him%20of%20his%20continued%20silence%20on%20the%20Manipur%20violence%2C%20which%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Congress%20leader%2C%20reeks%20of%20nothing%20but%20%3Cem%3Eahankar%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0(hubris).%20He%20spoke%20about%20how%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20was%20a%20humbling%20experience%20for%20him.%20His%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMMEK8T0u5nQ%5C%22%3Eexperiences%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20groups%20of%20marginalised%20women%20and%20deprived%20farmers%20in%20the%20Yatra%2C%20he%20recalled%2C%20made%20him%20sensitive%20to%20their%20grief%2C%20their%20problems%2C%20and%20their%20helplessness%20and%20how%20it%20crushed%20his%20ahankar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20have%20to%20listen%20to%20their%20voices%2C%20then%20we%20have%20to%20let%20go%20of%20our%20arrogance.%20When%20we%20do%20that%20we%20will%20be%20able%20to%20hear%20the%20voice%20of%20the%20people%2C%20and%20we%20have%20to%20%5Bdo%20so%5D%20by%20leaving%20behind%20arrogance%20and%20hatred%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gandhi%20retorted%2C%20implying%20that%20it%20was%20not%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20but%20Modi%20who%20is%20%E2%80%9Carrogant%E2%80%9D.%20He%20alleged%20that%20Modi%20has%20%E2%80%9Cmurdered%E2%80%9D%20that%20voice%2C%20and%20killed%20%E2%80%9CBharat%20Mata%E2%80%9D%20in%20Manipur%20and%20Haryana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20claimed%20that%20the%20BJP%20has%20put%20India%20and%20its%20voices%20on%20fire%20by%20sprinkling%20%E2%80%9Ckerosene%E2%80%9D%20from%20Manipur%20to%20Haryana.%20Flipping%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20accusation%20against%20INDIA%20on%20its%20head%2C%20Gandhi%20said%20that%20the%20saffron%20party%20leaders%20are%3Cem%3E%20deshdrohi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(traitor)%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%20a%20clear%20attempt%20to%20assert%20an%20inclusive%20form%20of%20nationalism%20as%20espoused%20by%20the%20INDIA%20parties%20against%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20muscular%2C%20Hindu%20majoritarian%20nationalism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fa-war-lies-ahead-of-rahul-gandhi-and-he-must-prepare%5C%22%3EA%20War%20Lies%20Ahead%20for%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20He%20Must%20Prepare%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnly%20recently%2C%20BJP%20MP%20Nishikant%20Dubey%20had%20called%20former%20CPI(M)%20general%20secretary%20Prakash%20Karat%20a%20deshdrohi%2C%20even%20as%20he%20made%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fcongress-leaders-meet-lok-sabha-speaker-om-birla-over-nishikant-dubeys-remarks-against-party%2Farticle67171554.ece%5C%22%3Esimilar%20allegations%20against%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Gandhi%20had%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20government%20for%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fthe-symbiotic-careers-of-modi-and-adani%5C%22%3Eproximity%20with%20the%20Adani%20Group%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20taking%20off%20from%20his%20sustained%20criticism%20of%20alleged%20cronyism%20under%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20leadership%20%E2%80%93%20a%20response%20to%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20remark%20that%20the%20INDIA%20parties%E2%80%99%20no-confidence%20motion%20was%20an%20attack%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics-and-nation%2Fthis-no-trust-vote-is-against-son-of-a-poor-bjps-nishikant-dubey%2Farticleshow%2F102531442.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Cson%20of%20the%20poor%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRavan%20would%20listen%20to%20two%20people%20%E2%80%93%20Meghnad%20and%20Kumbhkaran.%20Similarly%2C%20Modi%20also%20listens%20to%20only%20Amit%20Shah%20and%20%5BGautam%5D%20Adani.%20Hanuman%20did%20not%20set%20fire%20to%20Lanka.%20It%20was%20set%20on%20fire%20by%20Ravan%E2%80%99s%20arrogance%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gandhi%20had%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20was%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20arrogance%20that%20prevented%20him%20from%20visiting%20Manipur%20at%20a%20time%20when%20people%20from%20the%20state%20were%20facing%20their%20worst-ever%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20are%20anti-national%2C%20you%20cannot%20be%20%3Ci%3Edesh%20bhakts%3C%2Fi%3E%20%5Bpatriotic%5D%2C%20you%20cannot%20be%20%3Ci%3Edesh%20premi.%3C%2Fi%3E%20You%20have%20murdered%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gandhi%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20moniker%20INDIA%20was%20coined%20by%20the%20opposition%20parties%20after%20they%20navigated%20through%20their%20multi-layered%20differences%20to%20come%20together%20on%20a%20common%20agenda.%20They%20signalled%20that%20despite%20the%20mutual%20differences%2C%20the%20parties%20have%20united%20to%20battle%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20alleged%20onslaught%20on%20democratic%20practices%20and%20the%20constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGandhi%2C%20at%20the%20time%2C%20had%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20fight%20is%20against%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20ideology%20and%20its%20thinking.%20We%20have%20named%20our%20front%20INDIA%20because%20our%20India%20is%20under%20attack%20and%20we%20realised%20that%20the%20fight%20is%20not%20between%20two%20political%20formations.%20The%20fight%20is%20between%20two%20different%20ideas%20of%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20monsoon%20session%20was%20the%20first%20real%20test%20for%20INDIA%20to%20put%20up%20a%20united%20ideological%20front.%20Throughout%20its%20course%2C%20the%20grouping%20has%20taken%20a%20concrete%20shape%20in%20the%20way%20its%20leaders%20have%20coordinated%2C%20acted%2C%20and%20performed%20in%20unison%20during%20the%20monsoon%20session.%20The%20leaders%20have%20been%20meeting%20constantly%20to%20decide%20on%20their%20course%20of%20action%20every%20day%20in%20both%20Houses.%20They%20have%20also%20unitedly%20appeared%20in%20black%20clothes%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics-and-nation%2Fmonsoon-session-opposition-shows-up-in-black-to-protest-manipur-violence%2Farticleshow%2F102160820.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ea%20mark%20of%20protest%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20silence%20on%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20some%20debate%20on%20whether%20to%20move%20a%20no-trust%20motion%20against%20the%20Union%20government%2C%20they%20could%20stand%20together%20in%20the%20Houses%20once%20it%20was%20decided%20that%20the%20motion%20would%20be%20moved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGandhi%E2%80%99s%20speech%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20preceded%20by%20several%20such%20interventions%20by%20leaders%20of%20INDIA%20parties%20in%20the%20last%20few%20days%2C%20has%20shown%20that%20the%20bloc%20is%20resolved%20to%20take%20on%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20prime%20minister%20with%20aggression%20%E2%80%93%20an%20aspect%20many%20believed%20was%20missing%20in%20the%20opposition%20politics%20until%20recently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20parties%20will%20soon%20come%20together%20again%20in%20Mumbai%20to%20divide%20roles%20and%20responsibilities%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20INDIA%E2%80%99s%20effort%20will%20be%20to%20reclaim%20its%20pole%20position%20by%20asserting%20its%20idea%20of%20inclusive%2C%20redistributive%20nationalism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20may%20indeed%20turn%20out%20to%20be%20%E2%80%9Ca%20fight%20between%20two%20different%20ideas%20of%20India%E2%80%9D%2C%20as%20Gandhi%20had%20proclaimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691592286000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F09195446%2Fimage-1207.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frahul-gandhi-speech-ideology-india-alliance%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Congress%20leader%20not%20only%20laid%20down%20how%20INDIA%20parties%20considered%20'Bharat'%20as%20a%20union%20of%20diverse%20and%20equal%20voices%20but%20also%20how%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20decisions%20have%20been%20largely%20controlled%20by%20corporate%20interests.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frahul-gandhi-speech-ideology-india-alliance%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%20%7C%20Full%20Details%20of%20Kuki%20Leaders'%20Talks%20With%20Amit%20Shah%20on%20Mass%20Burials%2C%20Separate%20Administration%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F09200410%2FKT-9-August-2023.00_38_28_09.Still002.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20comprehensive%20and%20detailed%20interview%2C%20conducted%20immediately%20after%20the%20Indigenous%20Tribal%20Leaders%20Forum%20(ITLF)%20finished%20their%20talks%20with%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20the%20umbrella%20body%E2%80%99s%20spokesperson%20has%20revealed%20what%20was%20discussed%2C%20the%20positions%20taken%20by%20either%20side%20and%20the%20areas%20where%20there%20is%20agreement%20as%20well%20as%2C%20as%20he%20put%20it%2C%20one%20area%20where%20there%20is%20a%2050%3A50%20chance%20of%20an%20agreement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%2034-minute%20interview%20with%20Karan%20Thapar%20for%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Ginza%20Vualzong%20said%20the%20home%20minister%20has%20asked%20ITLF%20to%20find%20a%20different%20site%20for%20the%20mass%20burials%20they%20plan%20because%20the%20original%20site%20they%20have%20chosen%20is%20in%20the%20conflict%20zone.%20As%20a%20sweetener%2C%20Vualzong%20said%20Shah%20has%20offered%20to%20hand%20over%20the%20original%20site%20to%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20community%20to%20use%20for%20public%20utility%20purposes%20or%20as%20a%20memorial%20park.%20He%20believes%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20%E2%80%9C50%3A50%20chance%E2%80%9D%20the%20Kuki%20community%20will%20agree.%20ITLF%20will%20now%20consult%20them.%20He%20says%20they%20will%20communicate%20their%20answer%20to%20the%20Home%20Minister%20in%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVualzong%20said%20that%20in%20response%20to%20the%20ITLF%20demand%20that%20%E2%80%9CMeitei%20state%20forces%E2%80%9D%20should%20not%20be%20deployed%20in%20the%20hill%20district%2C%20the%20home%20minister%20agreed%20that%20they%20would%20only%20enter%20accompanied%20by%20either%20the%20paramilitary%20or%20the%20Assam%20Rifles.%20Vualzong%20said%20this%20was%20not%20what%20they%20wanted%20but%20they%20are%20prepared%20to%20accept%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegarding%20the%20ITLF%20demand%20that%20tribal%20jail%20inmates%20in%20Imphal%20should%20be%20moved%20to%20other%20states%20for%20safety%2C%20Shah%20said%20that%20as%20of%20now%20there%20has%20been%20no%20trouble%20or%20violence%20of%20any%20sort%20in%20jails%20%E2%80%93%20something%20Vualzong%20agreed%20with%20%E2%80%93%20but%20if%20anything%20were%20to%20happen%2C%20the%20government%20would%20shift%20tribal%20jail%20inmates%20out%20of%20Imphal%20jails.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20key%20issue%20of%20separate%20administration%2C%20Vualzong%20said%20the%20issue%20was%20raised%20with%20Shah%2C%20who%20said%20that%20it%20should%20be%20talked%20about%20after%20peace%20has%20prevailed%20and%20an%20appropriate%20political%20environment%20is%20created.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20the%20home%20minister%20is%20envisaging%20a%20two-stage%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVualzong%20said%20he%20got%20the%20impression%20that%20the%20director%20of%20the%20Intelligence%20Bureau%20and%20A.K.%20Mishra%2C%20the%20interlocutor%20for%20militant%20groups%20which%20have%20entered%20into%20a%20suspension%20of%20operations%20(SoO)%20agreement%20with%20the%20government%2C%20are%20sympathetic%20and%20understanding%20of%20the%20ITLF%20position%20that%20they%20cannot%20any%20longer%20live%20with%20the%20Meiteis.%20However%2C%20neither%20gentleman%20spoke%20specifically%20about%20a%20separate%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20spokesperson%20made%20clear%20that%20the%20ITLF%20will%20no%20longer%20accept%20an%20autonomous%20territorial%20council.%20That%20door%20is%20firmly%20shut.%20However%2C%20they%20are%20open%20to%20either%20separate%20statehood%20or%20un