0when%20to%20provide%20irrigation%20so%20the%20crop%20is%20not%20submerged%20in%20water%20all%20the%20time.%20With%20this%2C%20he%20is%20cutting%20down%2040%20percent%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F204393%2Findia-water-pumps-innovation-agritech-invention-irrigation-agriculture-farmers-kisanraja%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewater%20use%20in%20farms%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20technology%20helps%20farmers%20analyze%20the%20dynamic%20climatic%20conditions%20and%20plan%20their%20farm%20cultivation%20for%20both%20local%20and%20foreign%20crop%20varieties.%20It%20also%20helps%20them%20understand%20and%20reduce%20the%20possibility%20of%20disease%20and%20pest%20infestation%2C%20while%20also%20boosting%20the%20production%20cycle%20considerably%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Malesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWatch%20how%20he%20is%20revolutionising%20the%20lives%20of%20farmers%20across%20the%20country%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FsS95LtrgLgw%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26autoplay%3D0%26cc_load_policy%3D0%26cc_lang_pref%3D%26iv_load_policy%3D3%26loop%3D0%26modestbranding%3D0%26rel%3D0%26fs%3D1%26playsinline%3D0%26autohide%3D2%26theme%3Ddark%26color%3Dred%26controls%3D1%26%5C%22%20data-no-lazy%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Divya%20Sethu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691558309000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22http%3A%2F%2Fimg.youtube.co