%5C%22%3EHypothalamus%20offers%20disease-specific%20diet%20meals%20and%20general%20wellness%20meal%20services%20focused%20on%20holistic%20nutrition.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20tofu%20bottle%20gourd%20millet%20%3Cem%3Edosa%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20sesame%20green%20gram%20%3Cem%3Ekhichdi%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20bottle%20gourd%20brown%20rice%20%3Cem%3Edosa%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20cardamom%20milk%20%E2%80%94%20the%20meal%20package%20comprises%20breakfast%2C%20mid-meal%2C%20lunch%2C%20snacks%2C%20dinner%2C%20and%20a%20bedside%20meal.%20Delivered%20thrice%20a%20day%2C%20the%20six-meal%20package%20is%20priced%20at%20Rs%20600%20a%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20challenges%20to%20setting%20up%20such%20a%20business%2C%20Harsha%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CSince%20it%20is%20a%20very%20unique%20concept%2C%20it%20took%20us%20six%20months%20to%20understand%20the%20market%20and%20gain%20the%20doctors%E2%80%99%20trust.%20Given%20my%20age%2C%20they%20were%20doubtful%20if%20I%20would%20be%20able%20to%20manage%20the%20network.%20At%20first%2C%20managing%20the%20kitchen%20and%20chefs%20was%20a%20little%20challenging%2C%20but%20with%20experience%2C%20we%20were%20able%20to%20do%20better.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESri%20Harsha%20started%20the%20company%20with%20an%20initial%20investment%20of%20Rs%2015%20lakh.%20Today%2C%20the%20company%20generates%20a%20monthly%20revenue%20of%20Rs%207%20lakh.%20He%20aims%20to%20expand%20the%20services%20to%20Bengaluru%20by%20the%20year-end.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20vision%20is%20to%20provide%20end-to-end%20medical%20nutrition%20therapy%20to%20patients%20and%20promote%20general%20wellness%20for%20health-conscious%20people.%20I%20once%20needed%20such%20a%20service%20myself%2C%20and%20now%20we%20are%20witnessing%20how%20our%20nutrition%20support%20helps%20patients%20with%20diabetes%20manage%20their%20blood%20glucose%20levels%2C%20and%20malnourished%20children%20thrive%20and%20gain%20weight.%20This%20kind%20of%20positive%20imp