23%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpon%20successful%20completion%2C%20India%20will%20become%20the%20fourth%20country%20to%20achieve%20a%20lunar%20soft%20landing%20after%20the%20United%20States%2C%20the%20former%20Soviet%20Union%2C%20and%20China.%20Both%20the%20United%20States%20and%20the%20former%20Soviet%20Union%20failed%20many%20times%20before%20they%20successfully%20landed%20on%20the%20Moon.%20China%20was%20the%20only%20country%20to%20succeed%20in%20its%20first%20attempt%20with%20the%20Chang%E2%80%99e-3%20mission%20in%202013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691408722000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D326455%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chandrayaan-3%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20lunar%20mission%20launched%20by%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO)%2C%20recently%20shared%20some%20stunning%20captures%20of%20the%20Moon.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20what%20we%20can%20expect%20next.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F326455%2Fisro-chandrayaan-3-updates-first-pictures-of-the-moon-tweets-video%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BYOB%3A%20Friends%20Turn%207%20Lakh%20Glass%20Bottles%20into%20Quirky%20Art%20%26%20Home%20Decor%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EGayatri%20Fabian%2C%20based%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20affectionately%20labels%20herself%20as%20a%20hoarder%2C%20expressing%20her%20fondness%20for%20collecting%20items%2C%20particularly%20bottles.%20%E2%80%9CI%20can%20never%20have%20enough%20of%20them.%20I%20would%20go%20to%20scrap%20dealers%20and%20wander%20around%20looking%20for%20pretty-looking%20bottles%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20exclaims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20soon%20enough%20she%20found%20herself%20in%20a%20quirky%20predicament%20%E2%80%94%20her%20house%20had%20become%20a%20battleground%20of